                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-2">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/location.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Housing services</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-2">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/medical-history.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Assistance the admins</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-2">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/cheers.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Locals good deals</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-2">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/guitar.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Concerts</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-2">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/masks.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Cultural deals</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-2">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/museum.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Museums</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-2">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/football.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Sports</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Languages?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>French & English</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Why do you love Lille?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Belle architecture, ville jeune et dynamique avec de nombreux étudiants</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Your favorite spots in Lille?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>La citadelle pour courir, le nouveau siècle et la rue royale pour sortir le soir, et rue de gand pour les restaurants</p>
